    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Recorded replays</strong>: Video recordings of past Crazy Time rounds. You can watch but not participate. Not the live game.</li>
      <li><strong>Software simulations</strong>: Third-party apps or browser games that simulate a Crazy Time-like wheel with fake credits. These do not replicate actual Crazy Time math, RTP, or bonus mechanics. What you learn from them does not transfer to the real game.</li>
      <li><strong>Affiliate redirects</strong>: Pages labelled "free Crazy Time" that immediately redirect to a casino deposit page. Not free at all.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      None of these are the real game. The only way to experience real Crazy Time is through a licensed casino platform offering Evolution Gaming's live Crazy Time tables.
    </p>

    <StakeCTA variant="card" text="Start on Stake — Minimum $0.10 Bets on Crazy Time →" />

