    <p>
      If you're new to Crazy Time and want to learn it responsibly:
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>Read our <a href="/crazy-time-rules">rules guide</a> and <a href="/crazy-time-how-it-works">how it works page</a> first — 10 minutes of reading covers everything</li>
      <li>Use the <a href="/session-planner">session planner</a> to set your budget and rules before touching the game</li>
      <li>Watch 15–20 live rounds on Stake without betting — just observe</li>
      <li>If you're comfortable, start with $0.10 per segment bets for your first real session</li>
      <li>Follow the <a href="/crazy-time-bankroll-strategy">bankroll strategy</a> from session one — the discipline you build early stays with you</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
      Crazy Time is an entertainment product. The house has an edge of 4–6% — that's your cost of entertainment per session. Go in knowing this, plan accordingly, and the experience can be genuinely enjoyable.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      {[
        { q: 'Can you play Crazy Time for free?', a: 'No true free demo mode exists. Crazy Time is a live dealer game with a real physical wheel — it requires real money bets to participate. You can watch the live stream without betting on most platforms.' },
        { q: 'Is there a Crazy Time demo mode?', a: 'No. Evolution Gaming does not offer demo modes for any live dealer games. Sites claiming to offer free Crazy Time are showing recordings or third-party simulations that do not replicate the real game.' },
        { q: 'How can I learn Crazy Time without spending money?', a: 'Watch the live stream for 20–30 rounds without betting, use our free strategy tools, read the statistics and RTP guides, and study the game before depositing.' },
        { q: 'What is the minimum bet on Crazy Time?', a: 'On Stake, minimum bets start at approximately $0.10 per segment. This makes real gameplay accessible for under $10 of total exposure per session.' },
        { q: 'Are there bonuses to play Crazy Time with free money?', a: 'Some casinos offer bonuses applicable to live games. Always check whether Crazy Time qualifies, the wagering requirement, and any maximum bet restrictions before activating a bonus.' },
      ].map(faq => (
        <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-1 m-0">{faq.q}</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm m-0">{faq.a}</p>
